data.description: This beautifully appointed Aria floor plan, AND well maintained 3 BDR 2 bath SFH built in 2018, has all of the bells and whistles one could want! New roof with ARCHITECTURAL GRADE SHINGLES and equipped with extended Solar panels for low low electric bills. There are top of the line security systems and cameras in place; entire home is  on a water softener system, reverse osmosis for the kitchen faucet, ice maker and the water dispenser on refrigerator; upgraded SOLID SURFACE countertops and THERMORVISION POLYMER kitchen cabinet doors, open cabinet concept. Newer UPGRADED LG STAINLESS STEEL appliances, washer and dryer,  18” tile everywhere except the bedrooms, blinds on all windows, full irrigation system, electric garage door with opener, and the list continues. Open lanai and room for a pool. This home is centrally located on .25 acres and close to shops, restaurants and water ways in a great SW Cape Coral location right near Chiquita Blvd and Trafalgar Pkwy.
